title: Daleville VB sweeps; Cowan falls
text:
Daleville VB sweeps; Cowan falls The Star Press 10:17 p.m. EDT October 19, 2015 Lindsay Ingenito CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
VOLLEYBALL 
Lindsay Ingenito had 15 kills and 13 digs to lead Daleville past Eastbrook 3-0 (25-21, 25-11, 25-15). Zannah Weber dished out 26 assists, while Brenna Townsend added eight kills and eight digs. 
Despite a triple-double from Gabriella Harrington , Cowan dropped a five-set match to Union (23-25, 25-23, 25-22, 10-25, 15-11). Harrington tallied 12 kills, 19 assists and 20 digs, while Diana Campbell added 21 kills and 23 digs. Read or Share this story: http://tspne.ws/1LHqL52 TOP VIDEOS
